snippet.title: Rocket League Season 8 Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch the Rocket League Season 8 Gameplay Trailer!
Learn more here: http://www.rocketleague.com/news/hit-the-streets-in-season-8/

Rocket League is taking it outside! Explore the grassy Sovereign Heights Arena, rise through the tiers of a new Rocket Pass, and unlock two JDM classics—the Honda Civic Type R and Honda Civic Type R-LE! 

Season 8 hits the streets September 7.

Rocket League Season 8 Gameplay Trailer
https://youtu.be/cfsWDIheeH8

#RocketLeague #RocketLeagueSeason8 #Season8RocketPass
